{"tid":272482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Pay 加入「P2P」支付功能 朋友付款自動存入銀行","createTime":"2017-06-06T00:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T08:01:58.000Z","uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9d97432b3c2fa2420d4ed839da3c59b6caf61e","tid":272482,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"在 WWDC 2017 開發者大會上，大眾多新系統之中最備受注目的當然是 iOS 11。一如預測 iOS 11 將會加入大量全新功能，當中 Apple Pay 亦將不只再局限在購買上進行流動支付，如今更終於正式引入方便過數的 P2P 功能。<br />\n<br />\nApple Pay 全新的 P2P（person-to-person）支付功能，與 Venmo 及 Square Cash 相似。用家可以使用 iMessage 給朋友付款，並自動存入你銀行戶口上。如此一來以後朋友之間只要有 iPhone，食飯及進行活動時要夾錢將會更加方便。而且未來會增加 Apple PayCash 的虛擬咭，功能類似 Debit Card。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/06/06/apple-pay-to-add-p2p-payments/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2Fapple-pay-to-add-p2p-payments%2Fsoftware%2F&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bf3a320b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/06/06/apple-pay-to-add-p2p-payments/software/</a>"},{"pid":"7239369d6f0739de1a6dff31c1e93d731464203c","tid":272482,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有一半係android機，即係又玩自閉"},{"pid":"8695075da846f7b10d68187e963b4a35e452e0ef","tid":272482,"uid":29663,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個世界有一半係android機，即係又玩自閉</blockquote><br />\n你意思係android玩自閉？"},{"pid":"859fd8daf08bce7079d645b78c6be1fde06ac342","tid":272482,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個世界有一半係android機，即係又玩自閉</blockquote><br />\n你意思係android玩自閉？</blockquote><br />\nan狗智商真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44811318539812f0ff026f8b4d935be42ae063a","tid":272482,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2